== 音樂風格、音樂淵源與影響力 ==
[[File:20151113_Bochum_Slayer_Anthrax_0279.jpg|thumb]]
炭疽是促使[[速度金屬|速度金屬]]和[[鞭擊金屬|鞭擊金屬]]誕生的重要樂團之一，他們在早期專輯中展現了一種典型的金屬樂聲音，歌詞以幽默主題和參考漫畫書而聞名，和同時代其他樂團產生明顯的區別<ref name="Allmusic Bio">{{cite web|first=Stephen Thomas|last=Erlewine|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/anthrax-mn0000490952|title=Anthrax Biography|publisher=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]|accessdate=2013-03-04|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415100750/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/anthrax-mn0000490952|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據美國權威音樂雜誌《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的看法，炭疽是少數在1980年代獲得讚譽並重新界定音樂風格的重金屬樂團之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/artists/anthrax/biography|title=Anthrax Biography|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]|publisher=[[西蒙與舒斯特|西蒙與舒斯特]]|accessdate=2013-08-23|archive-date=2017-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171124054122/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/artists/anthrax/biography|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。創始成員史考特·伊恩和早期主要吉他手丹·斯皮茨的風格被描述為「激進、當頭棒喝」，他們的特色是運用快速[[強力和弦|強力和弦]]和[[效果器|效果器]]，塑造出音樂中的侵略感<ref>{{cite book|editor1-first=Pete|editor1-last=Prown|editor2-first=Harvey P.|editor2-last=Newquist|title=Legends of Rock Guitar:The Essential Reference of Rock's Greatest Guitarists|url=https://books.google.com?id=60Jde3l7WNwC&pg=PA228&dq=anthrax+musical+style#v=onepage&q=anthrax%20musical%20style&f=false|year=1997|publisher={{link-en|Hal Leonard Corporation|Hal Leonard Corporation}}|isbn=0-7935-4042-9|page=第228頁}}</ref>。音樂作家{{link-en|湯瑪斯·哈里森 (音樂作家)|Thomas Harrison (Author)|湯瑪斯·哈里森}}表示，炭疽受到[[龐克搖滾|龐克搖滾]]影響而以更快的速度來演奏金屬樂<ref>{{cite book|last=Harrison|first=Thomas|title=Music of the 1980s|url=https://books.google.com?id=MBEZBL7Dr7YC&pg=PA60&dq=anthrax+musical+style#v=onepage&q=anthrax%20musical%20style&f=false|year=2010|publisher={{link-en|ABC-CLIO|ABC-CLIO}}|isbn=0-313-36599-7|page=第60頁}}</ref>。

樂團1993年的第六張專輯《白噪音之聲》（其中一首歌曲是約翰·布希唱的），它將[[油漬搖滾|油漬搖滾]]和[[另類搖滾|另類搖滾]]融合在黑暗氛圍的金屬樂中。美國紐約的當地報紙《{{link-en|鄉村之聲|The Village Voice}}》認為，約翰·布希時期的錄音室專輯有更多[[蠱戮金屬|蠱戮金屬]]和[[另類金屬|另類金屬]]的特徵<ref name="villagevoice">{{cite web|first=Christopher R.|last=Weingarten|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2011-09-14/music/anthrax-and-joey-belladonna-keep-it-in-the-family/|title=Anthrax and Joey Belladonna Keep It In the Family|work=《{{link-en|鄉村之聲|The Village Voice}}》|date=2011-09-14|accessdate=2013-03-30|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219174506/http://www.villagevoice.com/2011-09-14/music/anthrax-and-joey-belladonna-keep-it-in-the-family/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年第十張專輯《鞭金崇拜》標誌著原主唱喬伊·貝拉多納和典型鞭擊金屬的回歸。雖然許多歌曲被歸功於整個樂團，但是在1985年第二張專輯《散佈病源》中，幾乎所有音樂完全都是由查理·伯南特創作的，而歌詞則幾乎完全是史考特·伊恩寫的<ref name="Songfacts">{{cite web|url=http://www.songfacts.com/blog/interviews/charlie_benante_of_anthrax/|title=Songfact Interview with Charlie Benante|publisher={{link-sv|Songfacts|Songfacts}}|accessdate=2017-05-28|archive-date=2018-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180812083153/http://www.songfacts.com/blog/interviews/charlie_benante_of_anthrax/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除此之外，約翰·布希在樂團任職期間，也做了一些創作貢獻<ref name="Songfacts"/>。

炭疽受到許多[[硬式搖滾|硬式搖滾]]的影響，他們在2013年迷你專輯《{{link-en|頌歌 (炭疽專輯)|Anthems (Anthrax album)|頌歌}}》中，收錄許多1970年代的經典翻唱曲，包括[[匆促樂團|匆促樂團]]、[[廉價把戲|廉價把戲]]、[[AC/DC|AC/DC]]、{{link-en|瘦李奇|Thin Lizzy}}、{{link-en|波士頓樂團|Boston (band)|波士頓樂團}}和{{link-en|旅行者樂團|Journey (band)}}的原創歌曲<ref name="anthems">{{cite web|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/anthrax-anthems-ep-artwork-more-details-revealed/|title=Anthrax: 'Anthems' EP Artwork, More Details Revealed|publisher=Blabbermouth.net|date=2013-01-15|accessdate=2013-03-04|archive-date=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004160303/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/anthrax-anthems-ep-artwork-more-details-revealed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。樂團也受到許多龐克搖滾樂團的影響，例如{{link-en|愚蠢敗類|D.R.I. (band)}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bravewords.com/news/dirty-rotten-imbeciles-d-r-i-to-release-new-ep-in-june-audio-teaser-streaming |title=DIRTY ROTTEN IMBECILES (D.R.I.) To Release New EP In June; Audio Teaser Streaming |publisher=Bravewords.com |date=2016-05-18 |accessdate=2017-01-15 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923122008/http://bravewords.com/news/dirty-rotten-imbeciles-d-r-i-to-release-new-ep-in-june-audio-teaser-streaming |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="knac.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=19887 |title=D.R.I. To Release New EP In June |publisher={{link-en|KNAC|KNAC}} |date=2016-05-18 |accessdate=2017-01-15 |archive-date=2016-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520124554/http://www.knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=19887 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、{{link-en|壞頭殼樂團|Bad Brains}}、[[性手槍|性手槍]]和{{link-en|宣洩樂團|Discharge (band)}}。{{link-en|傳統重金屬|traditional heavy metal}}樂團如[[黑色安息日|黑色安息日]]、[[接吻樂團|接吻樂團]]、[[猶大祭司|猶大祭司]]、{{link-en|鐵砧 (樂團)|Anvil (band)|鐵砧}}、[[鐵娘子樂團|鐵娘子]]和[[摩托頭|摩托頭]]都對炭疽有著舉足輕重的影響力<ref name="Allmusic Bio"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://bravewords.com/news/anthrax-guitarist-scott-ian-on-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-i-feel-like-theyre-never-gonna-let-kiss-in-which-is-pretty-lame-when-you-consider-what-theyve-accomplished |title=ANTHRAX Guitarist Scott Ian On Rock And Roll Hall Of Fame |date=2013-03-21 |website=Bravewords.com |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archive-date=2014-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814092417/http://bravewords.com/news/anthrax-guitarist-scott-ian-on-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-i-feel-like-theyre-never-gonna-let-kiss-in-which-is-pretty-lame-when-you-consider-what-theyve-accomplished |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1987年起，炭疽也與[[金屬製品|金屬製品]]、[[麥加帝斯|麥加帝斯]]、[[超級殺手|超級殺手]]並稱為「鞭擊金屬四巨頭」<ref>{{cite web|last=Chamberlain|first=Rick|title=Thrash big four tour: The stars have their say|url=http://www.musicradar.com/rhythm/thrash-big-four-tour-the-stars-have-their-say-256073/|publisher={{link-en|MusicRadar|MusicRadar}}|date=2010-06-21|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2020-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823180947/https://www.musicradar.com/rhythm/thrash-big-four-tour-the-stars-have-their-say-256073|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國商業雜誌《[[彭博商業周刊|彭博商業周刊]]》表示，炭疽是[[饒舌金屬|饒舌金屬]]和[[新金屬|新金屬]]的重要奠基者之一，影響了[[林普巴茲提特|林普巴茲提特]]和{{link-en|再無信仰|Faith No More}}這樣的樂團出現<ref name=BW_Heavy_Metal>{{cite journal|first=Thane |last=Peterson |title=How Corrosive Is Heavy Metal? |url=http://www.businessweek.com/bwdaily/dnflash/sep2000/nf20000926_614.htm |journal=《[[彭博商業周刊|彭博商業周刊]]》 |date=2000-09-26 |accessdate=2013-04-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20001017185126/http://www.businessweek.com/bwdaily/dnflash/sep2000/nf20000926_614.htm |archivedate=2000-10-17}}</ref>。根據{{link-en|尼爾森唱片市場調查系統|Nielsen SoundScan}}的統計資料，炭疽於1991年至2004年間，在美國賣出兩百五十萬張唱片<ref>{{cite web|title=Top-Selling Hard Rock Artists According To Nielsen Soundscan|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/updated-top-selling-hard-rock-artists-according-to-nielsen-soundscan/|publisher=Blabbermouth.net|date=2004-01-30|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225014210/https://www.blabbermouth.net/news/updated-top-selling-hard-rock-artists-according-to-nielsen-soundscan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在全球市場上則總共賣出了一千萬張唱片<ref>{{cite web|title=Anthrax Profile|url=http://www.nuclearblast.de/en/label/music/band/about/70967.anthrax.html|publisher={{link-en|Nuclear Blast|Nuclear Blast}}|accessdate=2015-09-25|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414191818/https://www.nuclearblast.de/en/label/music/band/about/70967.anthrax.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
